<mj-text>
    We have also launched a trade union wiki page <a href='https://wiki.ictunion.cz'>wiki.ictunion.cz</a>.
    You can log in to the wiki with your Keycloak account.
    Your username is the email under which you submitted your application to join the union.
    You can set a password using the "Forgotten password" function.
</mj-text>

